steps.name: Given  User launches the browser and enters the DsAlgo application url
When  the user clicks on Get Started button in the DsAlgo Portal
And  user clicks on Sign in link in the Home page
Then  the page title should be displayed as "Login"
When  the user enters Username and Password from "Login" and 3 in the Login form
And  user clicks on Login button
Then  the user should get tooltip message below Password textbox and data fetch from "Login" and 3
